Bathroom actually has room enough to do the deed in comfort. Kitchen sink faucet with pull out sprayer. The entry door has two steps up into the RV but no steps outside to deal with. Full electric awning which is just awesome. Don't think I'll ever have a manual one again. Has backup camera plus side turning blind spot cameras to let you know if some idiot is beside you while you're trying to turn. All tires brand new in late July. New air filter. Has huge rear storage space that will hold kids' bikes no problem plus lots more. Has a huge led light bar but one half is not working so sorry about that. The side that works could spot a moose from here to Yellowstone though! Please text or call for details and showing. Not yet winterized so you can take it camping this weekend!

Title: Schwinn varsity
text: Description  Here is an original February 1979 VINTAGE  (The mens SCHWINN VARSITY 10-speed road bike with 27" wheels. It is in the original and very appealing CAMPUS GREEN factory paint. If you like unique unrestored original bikes with BETTER FEATURES, this may be a great bike for you. With the insanely high price of gas (and the economy being bad) now is the time to ride a cool vintage bike!  *This bike has a cool mens original road bike frame and forks with original paint and decals, with a little wear cool and comfortable riding street bike style handlebars, wrapped hand grips, Schwinn neck, twin stick shifters, Schwinn derailleur, Center Pull brakes, Schwinn cruiser bike seat/saddle, bear claw pedals, and more!  This bike has the convenience of 10-speeds!  *Remember the Schwinn Continental and Varsity road bikes? EVERYONE wanted one back in the day! Now you almost never see them! Bring back some fond memories and create some great new ones as well!  *The tires are 27x1 1/4". The distance from the floor to the top of the seat post clamp is approx 34". The distance from the center of the crank to the top of the seat post clamp is approx 24". The center of the handlebar stem to the center of the seat post is approx 22". The bike will accomadate most any rider comfortably. The seat height is easy to adjust.
